		{"id":"group-frontend","type":"group","x":3280,"y":-238,"width":660,"height":821,"label":"FRONTEND (frontend/)"},
		{"id":"group-storage","type":"group","x":1280,"y":148,"width":420,"height":772,"label":"STOCKAGE (data/)"},
		{"id":"group-sources","type":"group","x":-2540,"y":160,"width":440,"height":700,"label":"SOURCES EXTERNES"},
		{"id":"group-config","type":"group","x":-1720,"y":-820,"width":450,"height":560,"label":"CONFIG & INIT"},
		{"id":"group-orchestrator","type":"group","x":-860,"y":40,"width":420,"height":500,"label":"ORCHESTRATION (core/)"},
		{"id":"src-youtube","type":"text","text":"## YouTube Data API v3\n\nOAuth 2.0 (subscriptions)\nClé API (trending)\nQuota: 10 000/jour","x":-2520,"y":190,"width":390,"height":135,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"core-config","type":"text","text":"## core/config.py\n\nCharge `config.yaml` + `.env`\nValidation au démarrage\nFail fast si invalide\n\n→ Retourne un `dict` Python","x":-960,"y":-780,"width":340,"height":220},
		{"id":"core-logger","type":"text","text":"## core/logger.py\n\n`StructuredLogger(component)`\nJSON structuré → fichier + stdout\nJamais de `print()`\n\n```json\n{\"ts\":..., \"component\":..., \"event\":...}\n```","x":-960,"y":-540,"width":340,"height":240},
		{"id":"core-categories","type":"text","text":"## core/categories.py\n\n14 catégories normalisées\nConstantes string immuables\n\n`youtube_subs`, `tech_ai`,\n`politique_ca`, `spatial`, etc.","x":-960,"y":-280,"width":340,"height":200},
		{"id":"main-py","type":"text","text":"## main.py\n\nPoint d'entrée\nCharge config → lance orchestrateur\nCron systemd 6h00","x":-840,"y":65,"width":380,"height":130,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"agent-yt-trend","type":"text","text":"### youtube_trending.py\nTendances par région\nClé API | cat: `youtube_trending`","x":-1525,"y":260,"width":285,"height":130},
		{"id":"agent-rss","type":"text","text":"### rss_generic.py\nAgent RSS réutilisable\n5+ instances via config\ncat: `tech_ai`, `politique_*`, etc.","x":-1525,"y":410,"width":285,"height":160},
		{"id":"agent-yt-subs","type":"text","text":"### youtube_subs.py\nAbonnements → top N par vues\nOAuth 2.0 | cat: `youtube_subs`","x":-1525,"y":115,"width":285,"height":120},
		{"id":"agent-local","type":"text","text":"### local_contrecoeur.py\nAvis municipaux, alertes\ncat: `local_contrecoeur`\n`local_alerte`","x":-1525,"y":595,"width":285,"height":175},
		{"id":"env","type":"text","text":"## secrets/.env\n\n`ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`\n`YOUTUBE_CLIENT_ID`\n`YOUTUBE_CLIENT_SECRET`\n`FLASK_SECRET_KEY`\n`AUTH_PASSWORD`","x":-1680,"y":-500,"width":390,"height":200},
		{"id":"config-yaml","type":"text","text":"## config.yaml\n\nConfiguration globale YAML\n- Agents activés/désactivés\n- Feeds RSS URLs\n- Poids du scorer\n- Voix TTS\n- Limites (top 30, max 60s audio)","x":-1680,"y":-780,"width":390,"height":260},
		{"id":"orchestrator","type":"text","text":"## core/orchestrator.py\n\n`ThreadPoolExecutor`\nLance tous les agents en parallèle\nTimeout: 5 min/agent\nSi 1 échoue → les autres continuent\n\nSortie: `list[RawNewsItem]` fusionnée\n+ `list[AgentReport]`","x":-840,"y":250,"width":380,"height":260,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"data-contract","type":"text","text":"# RawNewsItem\n\n**Obligatoires:**\n`title` `source_url` `source_name`\n`category` `published_at`\n\n**Optionnels:**\n`description` `image_url` `video_url`\n`video_type` `raw_content`\n`popularity_score` `metadata`\n\n**Ajoutés par le pipeline:**\n`summary_fr` `image_path`\n`audio_path` `final_score`","x":-860,"y":660,"width":420,"height":360,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# Flow de données — Code\n\nChaque boîte = un fichier Python réel\nChaque flèche = un type de données échangé\nDe gauche à droite : Sources → Collecte → Traitement → Stockage → Service → Affichage","x":-300,"y":-900,"width":600,"height":180,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"agent-events","type":"text","text":"### events_montreal.py\nScraping événements\ncat: `evenements_mtl`\n`musique_electro`, `humour`","x":-1525,"y":810,"width":285,"height":140},
		{"id":"agent-viral","type":"text","text":"### viral_trending.py\nGoogle Trends + Shorts\ncat: `viral`","x":-1525,"y":980,"width":285,"height":170},
		{"id":"base-agent","type":"text","text":"## base_agent.py\n\n```python\nclass BaseAgent(ABC):\n  @abstractmethod\n  def collect(self)\n    -> list[RawNewsItem]\n```\n\nInterface + contrat commun","x":-1525,"y":1180,"width":445,"height":240,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"feed-assembler","type":"text","text":"## processors/feed_assembler.py\n\nCrée l'entrée `daily_feed` en DB\nListe ordonnée d'IDs\nStatut: ready | partial | failed","x":-90,"y":1600,"width":500,"height":165,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"img-extract","type":"text","text":"### 4. processors/image_extractor.py\n\nog:image > thumbnail YT > 1re image\nPillow → JPEG 720px qualité 85\nFallback: image par défaut/catégorie\n\n→ `data/images/{id}.jpg`","x":-290,"y":1123,"width":400,"height":205},
		{"id":"summarizer","type":"text","text":"### 3. processors/summarizer.py\n\nClaude Sonnet | 2000 tok in, 300 out\nTemp 0.3 | Toujours français\nMax 4 phrases | Coût < $0.01/item\n\n→ Écrit `summary_fr` en DB","x":-50,"y":733,"width":460,"height":215},
		{"id":"core-pipeline","type":"text","text":"## core/pipeline.py\n\nEnchaîne les 6 processeurs séquentiellement\nChaque étape = un BaseProcessor\nLogs structurés à chaque étape","x":-100,"y":-350,"width":500,"height":170,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"dedup","type":"text","text":"### 1. core/deduplicator.py\n\nURL normalisée (exact)\n+ rapidfuzz titre > 80% (flou)\n\nEntrée: `list[RawNewsItem]`\nSortie: `list[RawNewsItem]` nettoyée","x":-50,"y":93,"width":460,"height":225},
		{"id":"tts-gen","type":"text","text":"### 5. processors/tts_generator.py\n\nEdge TTS (async)\nfr-CA-SylvieNeural\nMP3, max 60s\nTronquer texte si trop long\n\n→ `data/audio/{id}.mp3`","x":400,"y":1098,"width":340,"height":255},
		{"id":"scorer","type":"text","text":"### 2. processors/scorer.py\n\nFraîcheur (décroissance)\n+ Fiabilité source (poids)\n+ Diversité (pénalité même catégorie)\n+ Feedback utilisateur (boost/pénalité)\n\nSortie: top 30, aucune cat > 40%","x":-50,"y":403,"width":460,"height":250},
		{"id":"sqlite","type":"text","text":"## data/newsfeed.db\n\nSQLite 3\nSQLAlchemy 2.0 ORM\nAlembic (migrations)\n\nTables: news_items,\ndaily_feeds, feedback,\nuser_settings","x":1320,"y":178,"width":360,"height":230,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"models","type":"text","text":"## backend/models.py\n\nModèles SQLAlchemy déclaratifs\nChaque table: `id`, `created_at`,\n`updated_at`\nConversion RawNewsItem ↔ DB row","x":1320,"y":488,"width":360,"height":170,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"static-files","type":"text","text":"## Fichiers statiques\n\n`data/images/{id}.jpg`\n`data/audio/{id}.mp3`\nServis par Nginx directement","x":1320,"y":700,"width":360,"height":141},
		{"id":"flask-app","type":"text","text":"## backend/app.py\n\nFlask 3.1 factory\nGunicorn 4 workers\nNginx reverse proxy\nCookie session signé","x":2055,"y":716,"width":360,"height":110,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"health-report","type":"text","text":"## core/health.py\n\n`AgentReport`: name, status, items, duration, errors\n`PipelineReport`: date, agents[], totaux, feed_status\n\nGénéré après chaque run quotidien","x":1505,"y":1033,"width":350,"height":234,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"api-health","type":"text","text":"### api/health.py\n\n`GET /api/health`\nStatut agents, coûts,\nstockage, uptime\nJSON complet","x":2175,"y":260,"width":240,"height":240},
		{"id":"index-html","type":"text","text":"## index.html\n\nPoint d'entrée SPA\nLogin + fil de nouvelles\nVanilla JS (ES2022)\nPas de build, pas de npm","x":3315,"y":-217,"width":350,"height":186,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"js-app","type":"text","text":"### js/app.js\nInit, routing\n\n### js/api.js\nFetch wrapper + auth cookie","x":3310,"y":-17,"width":265,"height":220},
		{"id":"css-app","type":"text","text":"### css/app.css\nThème sombre\nCSS custom properties\nScroll-snap container","x":3315,"y":530,"width":360,"height":50},
		{"id":"js-feed","type":"text","text":"### js/feed.js\nScroll-snap navigation\nCompteur position\nCalendrier dates","x":3665,"y":8,"width":245,"height":170},
		{"id":"api-feedback","type":"text","text":"### api/feedback.py\n\n`POST /api/news/{id}/feedback`\n`{type: like|dislike,\n  comment: ...}`\n\n→ Stocké en DB\n→ Influence le scorer","x":2435,"y":257,"width":260,"height":243},
		{"id":"api-feed","type":"text","text":"### api/feed.py\n\n`GET /api/feed/today`\n`GET /api/feed/{date}`\n`GET /api/feed/dates`\n`GET /api/news/{id}`\n\n→ JSON: items[], date, count","x":2320,"y":-274,"width":230,"height":243},
		{"id":"api-auth","type":"text","text":"### backend/auth.py\n\n`POST /api/auth/login`\n`POST /api/auth/logout`\nMot de passe unique\nCookie signé Flask","x":2320,"y":-21,"width":230,"height":180},
		{"id":"js-ui","type":"text","text":"### js/ui.js\nCarte de nouvelle\nMenu options (⋮)\nLike/dislike, toast","x":3671,"y":379,"width":233,"height":140},
		{"id":"feedback-loop","type":"text","text":"## Boucle de feedback\n\nUtilisateur like/dislike\n→ Stocké en DB via API\n→ Lu par le scorer au prochain run\n→ Modifie les poids des catégories\n→ Décroissance temporelle","x":2365,"y":992,"width":400,"height":212,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"js-player","type":"text","text":"### js/player.js\nYouTube IFrame API\nHTML5 <audio> TTS\nAuto-play/stop au scroll","x":3318,"y":257,"width":250,"height":140},
		{"id":"src-trends","type":"text","text":"## Google Trends + YT Shorts\n\nContenu viral\nTendances du moment","x":-2520,"y":715,"width":390,"height":110,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"src-scraping","type":"text","text":"## Sites web (scraping)\n\nÉvénements Montréal\nAvis municipaux Contrecoeur\nbeautifulsoup4 + requests","x":-2520,"y":530,"width":390,"height":153,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"src-rss","type":"text","text":"## Feeds RSS/Atom\n\nTech/IA, politique (CA, QC, intl),\nvéhicules, spatial\nHTTP GET → XML → feedparser","x":-2520,"y":360,"width":390,"height":150,"color":"1"}
